To all noobs...if your using utorrent...go to preferences>bandwidth and set global upload rate to 25. set max number connections and max connected peers to 500 each...
This should make downloads faster. 
Also...use VLC player it's free and it plays almost anything you can throw at it with no problems.
Just some friendly advice. Hope it helps.
